.TH "mipi_dbi_buf_copy" 9 "mipi_dbi_buf_copy" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
mipi_dbi_buf_copy \- Copy a framebuffer, transforming it if necessary
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" mipi_dbi_buf_copy
.BI "(void *dst "  ","
.BI "struct drm_framebuffer *fb "  ","
.BI "struct drm_rect *clip "  ","
.BI "bool swap "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dst" 12
The destination buffer
.IP "fb" 12
The source framebuffer
.IP "clip" 12
Clipping rectangle of the area to be copied
.IP "swap" 12
When true, swap MSB/LSB of 16-bit values
.SH "RETURN"
Zero on success, negative error code on failure.
